<h4>Hidden Panels (<code>.Panels--hidden</code>)</h4>

<p>The hides all of the children panels unless given a <code>is-active</code> class. This can be used with the <a href="switcher.html">switcher</a> module to create simple tabs.</p>

<div class="c-example">
  <ul class="c-menu" data-module="Switcher">
    <li class="c-menu__item"><a href="#" class="c-menu__link">Panel 1</a></li>
    <li class="c-menu__item"><a href="#" class="c-menu__link">Panel 2</a></li>
    <li class="c-menu__item"><a href="#" class="c-menu__link">Panel 3</a></li>
  </ul>

  <div class="Panels Panels--hidden">
    <div class="c-panel c-panel--box">
      <p>Panel 1</p>
    </div>
    <div class="c-panel c-panel--box">
      <p>Panel 2</p>
    </div>
    <div class="c-panel c-panel--box">
      <p>Panel 3</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="c-code c-code--html">
  <pre><code class="html">&lt;ul class=&quot;c-menu&quot; data-module=&quot;Switcher&quot;&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;c-menu__item&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;c-menu__link&quot;&gt;c-panel 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;c-menu__item&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;c-menu__link&quot;&gt;c-panel 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;c-menu__item&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;c-menu__link&quot;&gt;c-panel 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;Panels Panels--hidden&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;c-panel c-panel--box&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;c-panel 1&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;c-panel c-panel--box&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;c-panel 2&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;c-panel c-panel--box&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;c-panel 3&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
</div>

